      <title>St. John of Sinai on Sorrow that Produces Joy</title>
      <link>http://feeds.ancientfaith.com/~r/AWordFromTheHolyFathers/~3/4K1UnMrGOno/st._john_of_sinai_on_sorrow_that_produces_joy</link>
